{"tid":90210,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"晨曦細雨　重臨在這大地　雲加孤孤單單躲避","createTime":"2017-01-22T01:21:21.000Z","updateTime":"2017-02-16T13:08:49.000Z","uid":44584,"like":6,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"f4b0f78fa2667412464d9fb4a8dc6ebe271e912b","tid":90210,"uid":44584,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-22T01:21:21.000Z","msg":"晨曦細雨　重臨在這大地　雲加孤孤單單躲避<br />\n轉身剎那　在這熟悉的路旁　察覺身後路人是你<br />\n如一套戲　重逢在這舊地　雲加不知怎預備<br />\n一些嘆氣　跟一串慰問　和隨便說一些讚美<br />\n<br />\n為何你眼光　年月未變　思憶怎麼要再返舊年<br />\n你說法比走的一晚　連綿夜雨　也似這天<br />\n更多更詳盡歌詞 在 ※ <a href=\"http://Mojim.com\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2FMojim.com&d=i8WUAnXc8SZEx4Gy6C0J8EsIbL4fERhwM0ZRx9Zc9p0%3D&h=84fb03b1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">Mojim.com</a>　魔鏡歌詞網 <br />\n<br />\n總要在雨天　逃避某段從前　但雨點偏偏促使這樣遇見<br />\n總要在雨天　人便掛念從前　在痛哭擁抱告別後從沒再見"},{"pid":"fe60e843968843dcd956702995a418eee8cfc6d2","tid":90210,"uid":37811,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-31T22:16:01.000Z","msg":"雲加好波"},{"pid":"7fd3d60d6ec97a1d64459bf2a5387a8d660f6736","tid":90210,"uid":40588,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-31T22:17:21.000Z","msg":"成段野剩係改雲加同法比<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"68d9216fa2dc3063946c723db649eb274976a5fc","tid":90210,"uid":6964,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-01T17:38:44.000Z","msg":"Ching ho ball"},{"pid":"e99556799834abea4865361cbf9f56c569f06f51","tid":90210,"uid":13281,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-01T19:00:45.000Z","msg":"倫敦細雨 唔贏就最驟忌 雲加孤單單準備<br />\n失分作客 令阿妓慘遭面黃 卻發覺輸後仍然第四"},{"pid":"42d5654ab83bec8d6688a0c60c8cba5ba1187f94","tid":90210,"uid":16960,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-01T19:09:33.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>倫敦細雨 唔贏就最驟忌 雲加孤單單準備<br />\n失分作客 令阿妓慘遭面黃 卻發覺輸後仍然第四